<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Issue Alert - CMS</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; background: white; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc3545, #c82333); color: white; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
        .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
        .alert-box { background: #f8d7da; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .issue-details { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; }
        .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 10px 0; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef; }
        .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
        .detail-label { font-weight: 600; color: #495057; }
        .detail-value { color: #dc3545; font-weight: 500; }
        .action-buttons { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
        .action-button { display: inline-block; background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: 600; margin: 10px; }
        .urgent-button { background: #dc3545; }
        .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d; border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚ö†Ô∏è Issue Alert</h1>
            <p>An issue has been reported with your package</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
            
            <p>We're writing to inform you that an issue has been reported regarding your package. Our team is actively working to resolve this matter.</p>
            
            <div class="alert-box">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #721c24;">üö® Issue Summary</h3>
                <p style="color: #721c24; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">{{issueType}}</p>
                <p style="color: #721c24;">{{issueDescription}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="issue-details">
                <h3>üì¶ Package Details</h3>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Package Reference:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{refNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Tracking ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{trackingId}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Issue Reported:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{reportedAt}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Issue Type:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{issueType}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #e7f3ff; border: 1px solid #b3d7ff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #0066cc;">üîß What We're Doing</h4>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #0066cc;">
                    <li>Our team has been notified and is investigating the issue</li>
                    <li>We will contact you with updates within 24 hours</li>
                    <li>If needed, we will arrange for re-delivery or alternative solutions</li>
                    <li>Our customer support team is available to assist you</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="action-button urgent-button">üìß Contact Support</a>
                <a href="tel:{{supportPhone}}" class="action-button">üìû Call Support</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">üìû Need Immediate Assistance?</h4>
                <p style="color: #856404;">
                    <strong>Email:</strong> {{supportEmail}}<br>
                    <strong>Phone:</strong> {{supportPhone}}<br>
                    <strong>Reference:</strong> {{refNumber}}
                </p>
                <p style="color: #856404; font-size: 14px;">
                    Please have your tracking ID ready when contacting support.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <p>We sincerely apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused. Rest assured that we are committed to resolving this issue promptly and ensuring your complete satisfaction.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for your patience and understanding.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>The CMS Customer Support Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>CMS - Courier Management System</strong></p>
            <p>Customer Support: {{supportEmail}} | {{supportPhone}}</p>
            
            <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
                <a href="#" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;">üìß Email Support</a> |
                <a href="#" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;">üí¨ Live Chat</a> |
                <a href="#" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px;">‚ùì FAQ</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 15px;">
                This is an automated message regarding an issue with your package.<br>
                For immediate assistance, please contact our support team.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 